    <div class="upcoming"> 
     <h3><a href="http://polymathic.usc.edu/content/about/article/gaps_in_communication_inaugural_polymathic_student_conference_apply_now">Gaps in Communication: Inaugural Polymathic Student Conference—APPLY NOW</a></h3> 
     <p style="text-align:center;"><img src="http://polymathic.usc.edu/images/article_images/Conferenceimage.jpg" alt="Gaps in Communication: Inaugural Polymathic Student Conference—APPLY NOW" class="sidebar" style="max-width:200px; border:1px solid #999;"></p> 
     <p> We are pleased to announce our inaugural polymathic student conference, which will be held on Catalina Island at the USC Wrigley Institute from April 10-12, 2015. The conference will explore questions of "Gaps in Communication," and how we might use polymathic approaches to solve some of the greatest communication challenges we face today.</p> 
     <p> We are now accepting applications for students who wish to be considered as participants in the conference. Applications are due by March 20, 2015. Read more for more information on the conference and how to apply.</p> 
     <a href="http://polymathic.usc.edu/content/about/article/gaps_in_communication_inaugural_polymathic_student_conference_apply_now" class="more">Read more</a> 
    </div>
