        The library is by definition a center of interdisciplinary inquiry devoid of disciplinary biases. The library and the polymathic academy form a metaphoric and meta-cognitive environment for integrated interdisciplinary study. 
        <a href="http://polymathic.usc.edu/content/about/the_academy_and_the_library">Learn&nbsp;more&nbsp;»</a>
