     <div class="update"> 
      <figure> 
      </figure> 
      <h4><a href="http://polymathic.usc.edu/content/about/article/article_polymathic_pizza_the_apocalypse_with_professor_thalmann">Polymathic Pizza: The Apocalypse with Professor Thalmann</a></h4> 
      <p> Join us Wednesday, March 4th to discuss The Apocalypse with Professor of Classics and Comparative Literature Greg Thalmann.</p> 
      <p> Our spring series Polymathic Pizza, Part II: Back to the Future continues with our examination of the human obsession with the end of the world.</p> 
      <a href="http://polymathic.usc.edu/content/about/article/article_polymathic_pizza_the_apocalypse_with_professor_thalmann" class="more">Read more</a> 
     </div> 
